🏁 JOY OF DRIVE 🏁

Some of you may or may not have heard but I will be partnering with @kwezzo on a new brand called Joy Of Drive ( @joyofdrive_ ) and our first big event will be at @v2lab Mystery Meat 6 on Oct 29, 2023. ✨

Can’t lie, I was in a dark hole with no motivation to continue on my own personal work and brand. I kept pushing myself but it just wasn’t working out so I took a break. That break turned into months and then into years. I know people kept asking me when am I releasing new merch, when’s the next Art Show, etc. Don’t worry though, now I got that flame again and I’m excited and motivated to start this new path with one of my close friends that I call brother. We can’t wait to show everyone what we are cookin’ 👨🏽‍🍳👨🏽‍🍳 

🏁 @joyofdrive_ 🏁 #JoyofDrive
